                    <tr>
                        <td bgcolor="#ffffff" align="left" style="padding: 20px 30px 40px 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 'Lato', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 25px;">
                            <p style="margin: 0;">Hi {{$mail_data['contributor_first_name']}},</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td bgcolor="#ffffff" align="left" style="padding: 0px 30px 0px 30px; color: #666666; font-family: 'Lato', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 25px;">
                            <p style="margin: 0;">Thank you for your contribution to the Cayman Islands Seafarers Registry! The information you've shared is invaluable to the preservation of our national culture and seafaring heritage so we want to sincerely thank you for helping us pay homage to those who paved the way for our beautiful islands. We look forward to learning more about {{$mail_data['seafarer_full_name']}} as their profile continues to evolve on the Registry!</p>

                            <p>While we are in the process of reviewing your seafarer submission, please keep this email handy to make reference to your unique Submission Number {{$mail_data['submission_number']}}. This number can be entered into the Registry's Search so you are able to view the status of your submission.</p>

                            <p>As the Registry Moderators, we are responsible for reviewing the contents of your submission to verify the information submitted is valid and also appropriate for public consumption. Once verified, {{$mail_data['seafarer_full_name']}}'s record will be available for viewing in the Registry online. Should we have any questions, we will contact you using the Contributor contact information provided.</p>

                            <p>To continue to learn more about our seafaring heritage, we also encourage you to visit the Cayman Islands Seafarer's Association located in Grand Cayman, and the Veterans and Seaman&#39;s Association of Cayman Brac.</p>

                            <p>CaymanKind Regards,</p>

                            <p>Cayman Islands Seafarers Registry Moderator</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr> 
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
